This file is curated manually and focuses on dependencies that
are either (a) non-trivially embedded in the binary or (b) carry
terms the user of a redistributed binary should be aware of.
It is NOT a full transitive go.sum audit — that is the
responsibility of automated SBOM tooling. It IS a complete list
of the "heavy" native libraries SwartzNet ships against.

