================================================================
Other Apache-2.0 / MIT / BSD dependencies
================================================================

The transitive Go module graph includes many other packages
under Apache-2.0, MIT, BSD-2-Clause, BSD-3-Clause, or ISC. Run
`go mod graph` + any SBOM tool of choice (e.g. go-licenses,
cyclonedx-gomod) for a complete machine-readable enumeration.
As of v0.3.0 the extractor hot path — PDF, EPUB, DOCX, ODT,
plaintext, subtitle, and chunker — is entirely covered by the
entries above plus the Go standard library.

No GPL, LGPL, AGPL, SSPL, BUSL, CDDL, or EPL code is linked
into the swartznet binary on the extractor hot path.
